  <brief_title>A Parental Educational Intervention to Facilitate Informed Consent for Pediatric Procedural Sedation in the Emergency Department</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Parental Educational Intervention to Facilitate Informed Consent for Pediatric Procedural Sedation in the Emergency Department</official_title>
